OL,3,CCampaigners 'devastated' as British
OL,4,CSign Language GCSE is scrapped
OL,6,FPlans to introduce a British Sign
OL,7,FLanguage (BSL) GCSE have been scrapped
OL,8,Fdue to "practical challenges".
OL,10,FQualifications Wales announced today
OL,11,F(3 October) that they have taken the
OL,12,F"difficult decision" to suspend the
OL,13,Fdevelopment of a made-for-Wales GCSE
OL,14,Fin BSL.
OL,16,FThe qualification has been in
OL,17,Fdevelopment since 2019 but was delayed
OL,18,Fdue to the Pandemic.
