OL,6,FThe National Deaf Children's Society
OL,7,Fhas accused the Welsh Government of
OL,8,F"going back on its word" stating the
OL,9,Fdecision will be "devastating" for
OL,10,Fcampaigners who have campaigned "for
OL,11,Fdecades".
