OL,3,CCampaigners 'devastated' as British
OL,4,CSign Language GCSE is scrapped
OL,6,FSusan Daniels, Chief Executive of the
OL,7,FNational Deaf Children's Society,
OL,8,Fsaid: "It was only yesterday that
OL,9,FCabinet Secretary for Social Justice
OL,10,FJane Hutt spoke of the 'provisions'
OL,11,Fbeing made by the Government to
OL,12,F'promote and facilitate the use of
OL,13,FBSL' in Wales. It seems they're going
OL,14,Fback on their word less than 24 hours
OL,15,Flater.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/10
