OL,3,CCampaigners 'devastated' as British
OL,4,CSign Language GCSE is scrapped
OL,6,FLindsay Foster, Executive Director of
OL,7,FSignature, the leading awarding body
OL,8,Fand provider of BSL said: "It's
OL,9,Fdisappointing that after so much work
OL,10,Fthis difficult decision has been made.
OL,11,FWe will be sharing with Qualification
OL,12,FWales our research on the demand for a
OL,13,FGCSE in BSL, as well as the evidence
OL,14,Fof sufficient teaching supply in Wales
OL,15,Ffor launch, which has been developed
OL,16,Fas part of the GCSE Coalition group
OL,17,Fwork.
