OL,3,CCampaigners 'devastated' as British
OL,4,CSign Language GCSE is scrapped
OL,6,FShe added: "Our goal is that every
OL,7,Fschool in the UK can offer BSL as part
OL,8,Fof their curriculum. Whilst we
OL,9,Fappreciate the introduction of BSL
OL,10,Fwithin Skills for Life qualification,
OL,11,Fthe lack of a BSL GCSE will be
OL,12,Fparticularly disappointing for the BSL
OL,13,Fcommunity who will not be able to
OL,14,Fstudy for a GCSE in their first
OL,15,Flanguage alongside their peers."
