OL,6,FA Welsh Government spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"Wales was the first country in the UK
OL,8,Fto include British Sign Language in
OL,9,Fits curriculum, and we understand
OL,10,Fthere will be disappointment about the
OL,11,Fdecision by Qualifications Wales to
OL,12,Fsuspend the development of a BSL GCSE.
