OL,6,F"However we are pleased they will
OL,7,Fcontinue to develop BSL units as part
OL,8,Fof the new Skills Suite qualification,
OL,9,Fto be available from 2027. Through
OL,10,Fthis new qualification learners will
OL,11,Fhave the opportunity to be able to
OL,12,Fdevelop their practical BSL
OL,13,Fcommunication skills for social
OL,14,Finteraction in everyday settings."
